Titolo: Mystaria: The Realms of Lore

Anno: 1995

Descrizione: Mystaria: The Realms of Lore, released as Riglord Saga in Japan, is a tactical role-playing game for the Sega Saturn. In late 1996 it was re-released as Blazing Heroes in North America. Its graphics consist of pre-rendered sprites and polygonal backgrounds. Its sequel, Riglord Saga 2, was released in Japan only in 1996.

Genere: Non specificato


Valutazione: N/A
